author: @liza_pet
text: EXO is my very first and only favorite band in the entire industry. It doesn't matter how many more years pass, EXO were, are and will be Kings of K-POP, Kings of Vocals, Legends and Discoverers of the 3rd generation. EXO, even after 10 years of career, are the most popular, sought-after and highly paid SM group. Yes, because they are their best band in the history of the company. EXO is the only band with such a variety of high-quality music, choreography and visual effects.

author: @liza_pet
text: IT's been 11 YEARS NOW, BUT EXO'S VOCALS ARE STILL THE BEST AND MOST SOULFUL I've ever heard IN THE ENTIRE K-POP INDUSTRY. And no, it's not an exaggeration or bias, it's THE PURE TRUTH.

author: @liza_pet
text: 11 years have passed, but I have said and will say EXO is a real diamond not only of SM but of the entire K-POP industry. Almost everything that is being done now is purely American POP songs literally licked from the West. EXO are one of the very few remaining who personify and preserve the real K-POP while continuing to keep up with the times. EXO music is beyond time and language barriers, so it was, is and will be.

author: @liza_pet
text:
EXO KINGS AND LEGENDS OF K-POP 
FOREVER ETERNA–A FACT THAT HAS 
NO LONGER NEEDS ANYONE'S APPROVAL.
POPULARITY AND LEGNDARITY ARE 
DIFFERENT CONCEPTS. Popularity is 
there today, tomorrow it is gone, and 
LEGENDARITY IS WITH YOU FOREVER. 
EXO songs released in 2012 in their 
debut album are relevant to this day. 
EVERY EXO ALBUM IS A VISION OF ART 
THAT YOU CAN LISTEN TO ENDLESSLY. 
EXO MUSIC IS TIMELESS. EXO ARE 
RELEVANT EVEN AFTER 11 YEARS 
OF CAREER.

author: @liza_pet
text:
EVEN AFTER 11 YEARS, EXO ARE THE 
KINGS OF THE VISUAL OF ALL K-POP.

author: @liza_pet
text: IT SEEMS TO ME THAT EXO IS ONLY GETTING MORE BEAUTIFUL EVERY DAY–THE GODS OF THE VISUAL OF ALL KPOP.

author: @liza_pet
text:
EXO is my very first and only 
favorite band in the entire industry.
EXO is not just my only love "all these 
boys are so dear to me as a family".

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just an incredible person that I will never stop admiring. At first glance, the album, the songs and his vocals may seem simple, but in fact it is not so at all. A large range does not make you a better vocalist yet, because another important role is played by the "technique", which Kyungsoo undoubtedly has great. He has such control over his voice that he makes all the transitions from low to high notes completely smoothly and even seems to make no effort. Quite naturally, during a song, it can change its timbre from incredibly sweet to sexually rude and sound simply amazing in each. Kyungsoo is one of those few vocalists who can make your heart flutter.

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

author: @liza_pet
text: I'm not a musician and I've never been a rap fan before I met Chanyeol because in my opinion he is the absolute exception from all rappers in the entire K-POP industry. Chanyeol has such a deep diverse voice that it is easy to adjust to the mood and feelings of any song.

author: @liza_pet
text:
I can't describe how much I love the voice and vocals of Chanyeol and this is the main rapper 
of the group that's what the KINGS OF VOCALS OF ALL K-POP means. Chanyeol has a great command of his voice and I really like how it 
can be from incredibly gentle and deep to rude and audacious. Always after listening leaving utter admiration THAT'S WHAT A TALENTED PERSON MEANS–TALENTED IN EVERYTHING.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Before meeting with Chanyeol, I could not 
even think that rap could be so diverse, 
it was he who showed me his entire palette.

author: @liza_pet
text: It's a terrible shame that even after 11 years of career there are "people" who underestimate the amazing vocals of Kyungsoo, which gives each song a unique zest and uniqueness.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Baby Kyungsoo is the cutest, polite, and humble idol in the entire K-POP industry. Although he does not consider himself cute and does not 
like to be called that, but it's the truth and he 
has absolutely nothing to do to be so cute. 
I love him madly for such spontaneity, sincerity and absolutely unique vocals that you can listen to endlessly.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Do Kyungsoo just has an unrealistically beautiful face and is literally getting more beautiful every day. He is exactly the kind of person who suits absolutely any style, hairstyle and concept, as evidenced by numerous EXO albums, numerous advertising and numerous acting shots of Kyungsoo, which are so different in a variety 
of roles and images.

author: @nouvincent5528
text:
-Xiumin who makes Chen laugh all the time. Just looking at him and listening to his beautiful voice gives me comfort, Xiumin we love you. 

-Suho gives us the best performance and the best scenes, and as always he says what makes the hearts of EXO-L flutter, and finally after filming he gives advice to our 첸첸. 

-the Perfect Hyun who sings passionately and shows all his skills through him, and yes listening to this song in the winter with EXO's winter songs would be something else. 

-Vocal King Chen♡ seriously, it has been a long time since I enjoyed the harmony of his voice with members especially Baekhyun and Kyungsoo, and he is getting more handsome by the day but he is also still the nicest of them. 

-But Chanyeol... just look at his breathtaking charm, he's so handsome and charismatic, and he and Sehun gave us one of the best rap parts I ever heard. 

-It's clear to all of us that Kyungsoo is super excited about the cb. I've been in love with him for a long time, but he's been making everyone fall for him lately, isn't he? Literally everything he does and says these days makes me happier. May he always remain as bright as he is now.

-Kai who I miss so much, we really miss you, but we're enjoying everything you've done for us now while waiting for you. 

-And finally our beloved Sehun whose parts in each song are my favorites. His shots were out beautifully.

I love you guys so much~♡
